# revora-extension

- MV3 extension: `inject.js` (MAIN world API intercept), `content.js` (panel + scroll), `background.js` (API uploads)
- Temu flow: click exact **"See all reviews"** → wait for `role=dialog` + "Item reviews" → scroll `div[data-scroll="true"]`
- Photos filter: click `Photos/Videos(...)` tab (`div._3bWZAd8u`) inside the dialog
- Review filters: `withText` (comment or translation), `withPictures` (pictures array + photos tab)
- Panel uses Shadow DOM for style isolation on `*.temu.com`
- `admin-bridge.js` on `admin.shopify.com` syncs Cloudflare tunnel URL to extension storage
- Reload extension at `chrome://extensions` after code changes; no bundler — plain ES modules